LAHORE, May 31 (APP): Punjab Chief Minister Sardar Usman Buzdar has expressed a deep sense of sorrow over the death of Khush Akhtar Subhani, MPA.
In a message, the CM extended sympathies to the bereaved family and prayed to Allah Almighty to rest the departed soul in eternal peace.
